      <h1>Testimonials: The Most Trusted Marketing Tool in 2025</h1>
      <p class="lead">Testimonials build trust, increase conversion, and humanize your brand. Learn how to use them in video for maximum impact.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>April 1, 2025</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated May 22, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
